caption.p: A. aegypti larvae morphology by SEM. Control ( A– C) showing no alteration on head (H), thorax (T), abdomen segments (AB), siphon (S) and anal papillae (AP). Larvae treated with nanoemulsion containing d-limonene at 250 ppm ( D– F) showing alterations on head (H), siphon (S) and on cuticles of abdomen (AB) and thorax (T).
